item.title: About
item.description: Hello! I’m Samuel Septimus Guyah, current Senior at Florida Atlantic University studying Computer Science. This blog contains my thoughts on Computer Science, Mathematics, Literature, Philosophy and generally any subject I find appealing to write about. I’m currently looking for both internships and full-time positions in the field of Artificial Intelligence so check out resume if you’re scouting for talent. You can reach me through my email and you can check out my github
